           SHORT="Software and text similarity tester."
cat << EOF
SIM tests lexical similarity in texts in C, Java, Pascal, Modula-2,
Lisp, Miranda and natural language. It can be used to detect potentially
duplicated code fragments in large software projects and to detect
plagiarism in software and text-based projects, educational and
otherwise.
EOF
